    • nextTask

      public io.vertx.core.Future<String> nextTask(Participant user)
      Logic here: In a random Experiment, we have callbacks for every step. So we need to mark every finished task. In a non random experiment, the final element needs to refer back to this, and if we get a callback in a non-random we proceed to the next element of this experiment.
      Specified by:

      Specified by:

      Parameters:

      Returns:
